---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Refund & Cancellation Policy | Bobo Analytics">
  <div class="policy-container">
    <h1>Refund & Cancellation Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: April 02, 2026</p>

    <section>
      <h2>1. Cancellation Policy</h2>
      <p>
        At Bobo Analytics, we strive to provide the best possible service to our clients. 
        You can cancel your subscription at any time through your dashboard or by contacting our support team. 
        Upon cancellation, your access will remain active until the end of your current billing cycle.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>2. Refund Policy</h2>
      <p>
        Since we offer a free trial for all our SaaS products (Bakery OS, Pharmacy POS, Grocery OS, etc.), we encourage users to fully test the platform before committing to a paid plan.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Subscription Refunds:</strong> Refund requests made within 7 days of the initial purchase or renewal will be considered on a case-by-case basis.</li>
        <li><strong>Processing Time:</strong> Approved refunds will be processed within 5-7 working days and credited back to the original payment method.</li>
        <li><strong>Non-Refundable:</strong> Fees for custom setup, data migration, or hardware integrations are non-refundable once the service has been initiated.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>3. Legal Entity</h2>
      <p>
        All transactions and services are provided by our legal entity:<br />
        <strong>CLINT MATHEW BOBO</strong>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>4. Dispute Resolution</h2>
      <p>
        Any disputes regarding payments or service cancellations should be directed to our support team at clintbobo54@gmail.com for immediate resolution.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .policy-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 60px auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #e2e8f0;
  }
  .last-updated {
    color: #94a3b8;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #94a3b8);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 900;
  }
  h2 {
    color: #6366f1;
    margin-top: 40px;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
    padding-bottom: 8px;
  }
  section {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
  li {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  strong {
    color: #fff;
  }
</style>
